Install Perl modules
~> sudo cpan App::cpanminus
~> sudo cpanm URI


http://bw2.local:81/?_escaped_fragment_=/#!/



To create snapshots:
--------------------
~> make-snapshot.sh 'http://bw2.local:81/#!/home'
~> make-snapshot.sh 'http://bw2.local:81/#!/aboutus'
~> make-snapshot.sh 'http://bw2.local:81/#!/courses'

* NOTE: Rename home.html --> index.html
* NOTE: Need ng-controller="MainCtrl" in index.html

